/* Table: "C_BoothDiscount" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "C_BoothDiscount"
(
"BoohtDisID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"MainDiscountID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"BoothID" NUMBER(32),
"BoothCode" VARCHAR2(20),
"IsNewBooth" INTEGER,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32),
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP,
constraint PK_C_BOOTHDISCOUNT primary key ("BoohtDisID")
);

comment on column "C_BoothDiscount"."BoothCode" is
'1009-A01-T8-00001
1009：商场编号
A：场馆
01：楼层
T8：标准展位
00001：逐一递增的流水号';

comment on column "C_BoothDiscount"."IsNewBooth" is
'10：是新展位
20：是旧展位';

comment on column "C_BoothDiscount"."Enable" is
'1：启用
0：停用';
